  "body": "Issue has been initially discussed here https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/issues/14798#issuecomment-1410980434\r\n\r\n**Steps:**\r\n1. User A sends CR to User B\r\n2. User B declines User's A CR\r\n3. See if User A is able to resend CR to User B\r\n\r\n**Actual result:** User A is able to spam User B with contact requests by removing and re-adding User B on profile page. \r\n\r\n**Expected result:** User shouldn't be able to spam other User with CRs after initial decline. See John's comment here https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/issues/14798#issuecomment-1406434296\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/97245802/215874144-bac51972-6ce7-4322-8046-6244b2b18170.mp4\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: nightly \r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Please, add logs/notes if necessary)\r\n\r\n",
